

1. Create new praritcle system
   Go to the menu bar and select GameObject > Effects > Particle System. and rename snow


Configure the Particle System 'snow':
1. set shape to box
change the scale x and z as 10

2 set start speed to 0

3 set velocity over lifetime to 'falling'
y axis as -5
click dropdown choose 'Random between two constants'
Y -1
  -2

4 increase emission to 100
rate over time as 100

5 set start size range[0.05, o.2]
click dropdown choose 'Random between two constants'

6 Set size over lifetime to 'fade away'
click size contain then go to setting

7 Add noise to create natural movement
strength as .2


